				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Since it is usually not known which individual RNA molecules will be analysed after samples have been archived at a biobank, tubes without blood cellular RNA profile stabilisers should not be used in biobanking. Storage conditions shall be documented. The temporary storage duration in the collection facility contributes to the total duration of storage.]]></text>
